               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184305080008"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was walking along Bishopsgate-street, and saw two boys run; hearing a cry of "Stop thief," I ran also, and was stopped; I had not been from home ten minutes.</p>
